comments.body:
Neither of those "errors" are errors. If you had tried to read the dialogue at all, you'd see that they're just asking you a question.

 

Please install an error handling addon like BugSack and post the actual errors that you're getting.

 

Also, please don't tag your issues as "waiting". Waiting means I'm waiting on you, not the other way around. If i see something tagged as waiting, I probably won't even open it.

> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
